name: Crossbreed goddess: CAPRICORN
description: In the battle of the titans, as they approached, Pan noticed the incident and warned the other gods, disguised as animals to protect himself from the monster. He tells them to enter. He tries to disguise himself as a fish.  But he can't quite change in a hurry, and his back is fish although the front part has not changed.  The Capricorn constellation is usually the forelegs of the goat that stick out from the tail of the fish is described.
